{"title":"hexo+git page 建站总结","uid":"fcce2594ca0a162d995a94852cfadb53","slug":"post-001","date":"2023-01-31T10:46:55.000Z","updated":"2023-02-01T02:47:47.525Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/post-001.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://gitee.com/zhaolu1466067009/picserver/raw/master/typora/5133.png","content":"<h2 id=\"概述：\"><a href=\"#概述：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"概述：\"></a>概述：</h2><p>​        本文记录了使用Hexo框架+git page搭建个人博客的流程，只需几分钟就可以生成并托管自己的博客文章</p>\n<h2 id=\"流程：\"><a href=\"#流程：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"流程：\"></a>流程：</h2><h3 id=\"安装Hexo依赖软件\"><a href=\"#安装Hexo依赖软件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装Hexo依赖软件\"></a>安装Hexo依赖软件</h3><ul>\n<li>Node.js (建议使用12.0以上版本)</li>\n<li>Git</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"安装结果检验\"><a href=\"#安装结果检验\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装结果检验\"></a>安装结果检验</h3><ul>\n<li>打开Git Bash或者cmd</li>\n<li>node -v</li>\n<li>npm -v<br>若正常显示出node和npm的版本 安装成功</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"安装淘宝镜像源\"><a href=\"#安装淘宝镜像源\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装淘宝镜像源\"></a>安装淘宝镜像源</h3><p>在Git Bash中运行如下命令：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">npm install -g cnpm --registry&#x3D;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;registry.npm.taobao.org</code></pre>\n<p>安装后查看当前版本命令：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">cnpm -v</code></pre>\n<p>安装淘宝镜像源的目的:提高下载速度</p>\n<h3 id=\"安装Hexo-cli\"><a href=\"#安装Hexo-cli\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装Hexo-cli\"></a>安装Hexo-cli</h3><p>在Git Bash中执行如下命令安装Hexo客户端：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">cnpm install -g hexo-cli</code></pre>\n<p>查看Hexo版本：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo -v</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"创建并初始化Blog文件\"><a href=\"#创建并初始化Blog文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"创建并初始化Blog文件\"></a>创建并初始化Blog文件</h3><p>管理员模式下在Git Bash中执行如下命令：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo init</code></pre>\n<p>使用本地端口部署页面：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo s</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"将文件部署到github上\"><a href=\"#将文件部署到github上\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"将文件部署到github上\"></a>将文件部署到github上</h3><ul>\n<li><p>在github上新建库，库名必须和自己github的id相同<img src=\"https://gitee.com/zhaolu1466067009/picserver/raw/master/typora/pic1.png\" alt=\"pic1\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>在blog目录下安装git部署插件：</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">cnpm install --save hexo-deployer-git</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>设置_config.yml</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\">deploy: \ntype: git\nrepo: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;looe327&#x2F;looe327.github.io.git\nbranch: master</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>部署：</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo d</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"参考文献-x2F-视频：\"><a href=\"#参考文献-x2F-视频：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"参考文献&#x2F;视频：\"></a>参考文献&#x2F;视频：</h2><p><a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Yb411a7ty/\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Yb411a7ty/</a></p>\n","text":"概述：​ 本文记录了使用Hexo框架+git page搭建个人博客的流程，只需几分钟就可以生成并托管自己的博客文章 流程：安装Hexo依赖软件 Node.js (建议使用12.0以上版本) Git 安装结果检验 打开Git Bash或者cmd node -v npm -v若正常显...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":757,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"hexo","slug":"hexo","count":1,"path":"api/tags/hexo.json"},{"name":"git","slug":"git","count":1,"path":"api/tags/git.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%A6%82%E8%BF%B0%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">概述：</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">流程：</span></a><ol class=\"